Package com.github.yeetmanlord.reflection_api.mappings

Class Mappings

java.lang.Object
com.github.yeetmanlord.reflection_api.mappings.Mappings
public class Mappings extends Object
Mappings are for getting changing nms class names, method names, and field names over different versions. It is very important that you use this plugin within the supported version range because if not mappings will not function properly.
Author:
YeetManLord
API Note:
Examples:
To get a class name use ClassNameMapping.getNMSClassMapping()
To get a field name use FieldMapping.getField(com.github.yeetmanlord.reflection_api.NMSObjectReflection)
To invoke a method without arguments use ArgumentlessMethodMapping.runMethod(com.github.yeetmanlord.reflection_api.NMSObjectReflection)
To invoke a method with arguments use ArgumentMethodMapping.runMethod(com.github.yeetmanlord.reflection_api.NMSObjectReflection, Object...)

  • Method Details

    • loadMappings

      public static void loadMappings() throws MappingsException
      Loads all mappings once the server version has been found. This is called in the ReflectionApi.init(JavaPlugin) method.
      Throws:
      MappingsException - Throws if the mappings failed to load.
      See Also:
      • ReflectionApi.init(JavaPlugin)
